    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to get the job done? This car is in honest, fair condition and offers fantastic value for anyone seeking a practical daily driver! It shows some expected signs of use and character from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, functional choice that's eager for its next adventure. A great opportunity to own a reliable ride at a budget-friendly price!",
      "price": 18500.0,
